text: Hypolytrum subcompositus is a species of plant in the family Cyperaceae. It is endemic to Cameroon. Its natural habitat is subtropical or tropical moist montane forests. It is threatened by habitat loss. ==References== Category:Cyperaceae Category:Flora of Cameroon Category:Critically endangered plants Category:Plants described in 2006 Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
